<H2>Research Interests:</H2>

<UL>
<LI>Query by content in multimedia databases; </LI>

<LI>searching in text and DNA databases; </LI>

<LI>geographic information systems; </LI>

<LI>fractals for clustering and spatial access methods; </LI>

<LI>declustering; </LI>

<LI>medical image databases. </LI>
</UL>

